00:17:53.990 --> 00:17:54.883
So let's look for them.

00:17:54.883 --> 00:17:56.440
Let's do the surveys.

00:17:56.440 --> 00:17:57.646
Let's build the telescopes.

00:17:57.646 --> 00:17:59.510
Let's put this telescope in space.

00:17:59.510 --> 00:18:02.010
That will be a major contribution

00:18:02.010 --> 00:18:04.780
to understanding the
threat from the asteroids.

00:18:04.780 --> 00:18:08.390
And then when we find a particular object

00:18:08.390 --> 00:18:11.960
that looks especially dangerous,
